article_title: Viewpoints: Lack of doctors in Humboldt reflects rural problems with access to health care
article_text: Humboldt County is a place of stunning physical beauty, a stark contrast to its residents’ astoundingly poor physical health. State data show the county at or near the bottom of health/wellness measures in virtually every category.
